       awaits you. Should you wish to experience a beautiful lunch by the
       sea... #ChevalBlancStTropez #Lunch #Pleasure
     * Happy mother's day! Come and find your favourite fragrance at
       Cheval Blanc Spa Ready to embark on a sensory journey?
       #ChevalBlancStTropez #Mothersday #Guerlain
     * The simple joy of having breakfast under the pines and by the sea
       So good to be back in #SaintTropez! #ChevalBlancStTropez #Provence
     * Last preparations in our 3 MICHELIN stars restaurant @lavaguedor
       Few hours left before beginning a promising 2019 season
       #ChevalBlancStTropez #Opening #Countdown

